d below the plane should have large radial velocities,\nclose to $\\sim$ 500 km/s in the present-day direction of the globular cluster\nNGC 6101.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Jun 2023 10:22:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-06"}
